caption: ⚡ In the neon-lit rain of New Avalon, Sereia Kade, a cyberpunk siren, struts through the wet streets, her sleek cutie-cut jacket shimmering under holographic glare, capturing the city's pulse. She wields a pulse-boost rifle, firing neon-dazzle into the midnight haze. Her daring silhouette is a siren in the concrete jungle, a digital rebel with a touch of sensuality. #Cyberpunk #FutureFashion #NeonAesthetics #DigitalInfluencer
